      <ResourceName>Ulysses URAP RAR 10 min. Electric Field Data</ResourceName>
      <ReleaseDate>2020-07-07T21:15:50Z</ReleaseDate>
      <Description>This set of RAR (Radio Astronomy Receiver) data from the Ulysses URAP (Unified Radio and Plasma Waves) experiment contains averaged value frequency spectra for electric field intensities in 10-minute intervals via CDAWeb. The frequency spectra are determined from measurements on the X antenna of the URAP instrument in units of microvolt/Hz^0.5 for the frequency channel from 1.25 - 940.0 kHz.</Description>
